7T_YtklLyyo.title: Waterflame - Glorious morning
7T_YtklLyyo.description: 2013 UPDATE!: I finally revisited this track! You can find the new version of this song on the Original official soundtrack i made for the Xbox360 game Castlestorm! follow the link:http://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=...-----Made in 2007!Made in FL5.This track has a long history of development. it started out as a small victory fanfare for a game called mecha pumble, but i liked the clip so much after finishing it that i decided to try to make something more of it. the original song is about twice in length,  but pulled out / just has more of the same. later when the contest for castlecrashers songs came up, i cleaned it up into a loop and submitted it, i figured it would go well for something of an intro. i placed 4th, if i recall correctly.later this song was used in a few flash games, like for instance, age of war.Now a final remake is in production, but until then, enjoy this, almost classic tune by now ;)go here for higher quality ver. and download. don't forget to vote if you download it!: http://www.newgrounds.com/audio/liste...▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔Facebook     ▸ https://www.facebook.com/Waterflamewo...WF Official    ▸ http://www.waterflamemusic.com/Newgrounds ▸ http://www.waterflame.newgrounds.com/Twitter     ▸ https://www.twitter.com/WaterflameMusicDeviant     ▸ https://waterflame89.deviantart.com/Google+     ▸ https://plus.google.com/+Waterflamemu...Bandcamp    ▸ http://www.waterflame.bandcamp.com/SoundCloud  ▸ https://soundcloud.com/waterflame89Spotify     ▸https://open.spotify.com/artist/7biIl...▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔▔
